# Provider hosts the pod is allowed to reach (POSIX extended regex, one per line) — the upstreams
# the pod's in-process key proxy forwards to. The eval uses the OpenAI path. MinIO is NOT listed:
# the pod reaches it directly on the internal network (see NO_PROXY in docker-compose.agent.yml),
# so it never transits this proxy.
^api\.openai\.com$
^api\.anthropic\.com$
